Package hexanome.fourteen.server.model.sent

Record Class SentGameBoard

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
hexanome.fourteen.server.model.sent.SentGameBoard
Record Components:
playerTurnid - The player's user ID whose turn it is.
availableNobles - The available nobles.
availableCities - The available cities.
availableGems - The gems in the bank.
cards - The cards that are face up.
expansions - The expansions for the game.
leadingPlayer - The current leading player.
players - The players.
gameid - The game ID.
creator - The creator.
isLastRound - Is it the last round of the game.
isGameOver - Is the game over.
